high_descs: Turn to the right and face the oven then make another right and move forward to the sink.
Pick up a black mug from the sink.
Turn around and step to the left with the mug.
Heat the mug in the microwave then take it out.
Look up at the cabinets above the microwave.
Place the mug inside the cabinet above the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Heat a mug and put it away.

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to the sink
Pick up the black coffee mug that is sitting in the sink
Take a step to the left and continue to stand facing the sink, and now the microwave too
Open the microwave and place the mug inside the microwave then close the door and turn it on. Then open the microwave and pick up the mug and close the door
Continue stand in front of the microwave and the sink but look up the the cabinets above
Open the left cabinet and place the coffee mug inside then close the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Place a heated coffee mug into a cabinet

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the stove, then turn to your right again and walk across the room to the sink.
Pick up the black coffee cup to the left of the blue plate from the inside of the sink.
Move over to your left so that you are in front of the microwave, on the counter, to your left.
Place the coffee cup in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the coffee cup from the microwave.
Move up so you can reach the kitchen cabinets above the microwave.
Place the coffee cup in the right cabinet, above the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm coffee cup in the cabinet.
